abstract: Photographer Joseph Swide captures images of Erasmus Hall high-school football team The Dutchmen in Midwood, Brooklyn; team is frequent competitor in Public Schools Athletic League championships.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Swide, a photographer and a former high school football player from Oregon, chronicled the 10-4 season of Erasmus Hall’s Dutchmen, from Midwood, Brooklyn.

headline.main: Joseph Swide Captures the Heartache of High School Football
